  "texts": [
    "Subsequently, we discuss the selection of keywords for the extraction of relevant information from the target-related literature.",
    "We conducted three independent experiments to assess the effectiveness of GIX.",
    "The first experiment (Exp1) demonstrated the Relation Extraction Capability (Stage-2) of the GIX framework using four well-known benchmark datasets for gene/protein interactions.",
    "The second experiment (Exp2) evaluated automated extraction using GIX against the manual curation of a benchmark dataset.",
    "The third experiment (Exp3) evaluated GIX against the manual curation of a real-world database of transcriptional regulations."
